name: Baseball Swing Ball Batter
description: Here is something interesting to me. For a baseball batter to be a decent hitter he should be batting around .260. That means out of 10 times at bat he gets a hit 2.6 times. Applying that to the five previous videos at least one of them should be descent, -  supposed to be. I wonder which one is that. 10.8 MB (11,387,813 bytes) GIF file
